%N A394298 a(n) is the number of unit cubes in the cubic lattice, divided by 2, that have at least one vertex strictly inside and at least one vertex strictly outside the sphere (x-1/2)^2 + (y-1/2)^2 + (z-1/2)^2 = n, i.e., the sphere centered at the deep hole.
%F A394298 a(n) == 1 (mod 12) for n>0.
